data.description: Welcome to 214 Yaupon, where waterfront living meets modern comfort in this 3-bedroom, 2-bath situated along a serene canal off Burnet Bay. This exquisite residence boasts a beautiful kitchen, granite countertops, creating a perfect space for entertaining. The primary bedroom provides a private oasis with panoramic water views and a luxurious en-suite bathroom. Step outside to a patio overlooking the canal, offering the outdoor for barbecues and relaxation. With a private dock for direct water access, this home invites you to embrace the outdoor lifestyle. Don't miss the chance to make 214 Yaupon your waterfront dream home.
